        <p class="p_Comment"><span class="f_TitreReleaseNote">Enhancement of connection type variables:</span> When a user previously modified the connection
		type by rules through variables <span class="f_Variables">Assembly1</span> and <span
        class="f_Variables">Assembly2</span>, this had no consequence onto the design created, as for information only.</p>

        <p class="p_Comment">You may now modify those variables by rules and see consequences straight onto the drawing of the design, as well as into
		computation from Components tab.</p>

        <p class="p_Comment"> </p>

