                style="color: rgb(0, 100, 255);">10 * touvcherd sub-side number into found shape (C)</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr align="left" valign="top">
              <td style="width: 735px;" width="735"><p class="p_Comment"
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 66px;"><span
                style="color: rgb(0, 100, 255);">+ unit (touched side number into found shape)</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr align="left" valign="top">
              <td style="width: 735px;" width="735"><p class="p_Comment"
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 66px;"><span
                style="color: rgb(0, 100, 255);">+ 0,1 * touched sub-side number into tested shape (C)</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr align="left" valign="top">
              <td style="width: 735px;" width="735"><p class="p_Comment"
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 66px;"><span
