		<p>Extrait les informations générales de la forme du tableau de forme,
        après une instruction <span class="f_Variables"><img src="img/OIForm.png"
        alt="OIF" border="0" height="20" width="20">GetShapeInfo
        - PointContainedIntoShape ()</span>, <span class="f_Variables"><img
        src="GPDForm.png" alt="GPDF" border="0" height="20"
        width="20">GenerateProfilesIntoShape ()</span> or <span
        class="f_Variables"><img src="img/OILForm.png" alt="OILF" border="0"
        height="20" width="20">GetBoardShapeInfo ()</span> during current computation. Only information marked with corresponding sign are generated by the
		instruction.</p>
				
        <p class="p_Comment"> </p>

		<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
        style="border: none border-spacing:0px;">
          <tbody>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
