                style="font-style: italic;">- setting</span></p>
              </td>
              <td width="1200" style="width: 1200px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><span
                class="f_ImageCaption">Type of information required. Returned values :</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
		  </tbody>
		</table>

        <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="border: none border-spacing:0px;">
          <tbody>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="4000" style="width: 4000px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 50px;">* 1 : <img src="img/OIForm.png" alt="OIF" border="0" height="20" width="20"><img src="img/GPDForm.png" 
				alt="GPDF" border="0" height="20" width="20"> shape number into the list of WinPro's available shapes, value 37 is for free shape.</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
