        <p>Transformation of a defined shape into a rectangle containing the shape. It is not the smallest rectangle around the shape here, but the smallest "flat" rectangle
		composed of verticals and horizontals.</p>

        <p class="p_Comment"> </p>

		<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
        style="border: none border-spacing:0px;">
