              </td>
              <td width="1200" style="width: 1200px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><span
                class="f_ImageCaption">Shape to be transformed into a rectangle containing the shape.</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
		
        <p>Returns <span class="f_Variables">True</span> or <span class="f_Variables">False</span> when transformation is a success or not.</p>

        <p class="p_Comment"> </p>


        <p class="p_Comment"> </p>
		
