            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        </div>

        <p>Transformation of a shape into a rectangle containing the shape. It is a rectangle according a given angle which is considered here, either the angle of the shape of
		label 2000, or an agle manually set.</p>

        <p>When <span class="f_Variables">"With angle = True"</span>, the angle should be set through the third setting.
        Otherwise if <span class="f_Variables">"With angle = False"</span>, the slope angle of side of label 2000 is used (angle beween the start of the first and the end of
		the last of label 2000)</p>

        <p class="p_Comment"> </p>

