                class="f_ImageCaption">En fonction de la forme, il faut donner
                son orientation, <span class="f_Variables">Gauche</span> ou
                <span class="f_Variables">Droite</span>.</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="229" style="width: 229px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 23px;"><span
                style="font-style: italic;">- Nom de la forme</span></p>
              </td>
              <td width="800" style="width: 800px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><span
                class="f_ImageCaption">Par exemple <span
                class="f_Variables">Rectangle</span>, <span
                class="f_Variables">Trapèze</span>. Voir <a
                href="rn642x.php">note de version 6.4.24</a>.</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="229" style="width: 229px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 23px;"><span
                style="font-style: italic;">- DimA à DimL</span></p>
