        <p class="p_Comment"> </p>

        <p>This instruction corresponds to <span class="f_Variables">SetupShapeInfo ()</span> à 5 paramètres de
        Winpro.</p>

        <p>with 5 settings into Winpro, and allows integrating, replacing. a segment.</p>

        <p>Attention, a 4 settings syntax instruction is needed before and after to grant and close modification, grant modification with type « -200 » then finalize with
		closing shape definition with type « -100 ».</p>

        <p class="p_Comment"> </p>

		<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"
        style="border: none border-spacing:0px;">
          <tbody>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="229" style="width: 229px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 23px;"><span
                style="font-style: italic;">- Shape index</span></p>
              </td>
              <td width="1200" style="width: 1200px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><span
                class="f_ImageCaption">Shape to be modified.</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="229" style="width: 229px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 23px;"><span
                style="font-style: italic;">- Segment index</span></p>
              </td>
              <td width="1200" style="width: 1200px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><span
                class="f_ImageCaption">Segment number to be modified in absolute, corresponds to absolute sub side number.</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="229" style="width: 229px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 23px;"><span
                style="font-style: italic;">- , , </span></p>
              </td>
              <td width="1200" style="width: 1200px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><span
                class="f_ImageCaption">!!! Unused, leave this setting empty !!!</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="229" style="width: 229px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 23px;"><span
                style="font-style: italic;">- InfoOperation</span></p>
              </td>
              <td width="1200" style="width: 1200px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 0px;"><span
                class="f_ImageCaption">Operation type.</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="border: none border-spacing:0px;">
          <tbody>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="4000" style="width: 4000px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 50px;">* 0 to add a segment at the end (« segment n°» ignored).</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="4000" style="width: 4000px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 50px;">* 1 to overwrite a segment.</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="4000" style="width: 4000px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 50px;">* 2 to insert a segment.</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top" align="left">
              <td width="4000" style="width: 4000px;"><p
                style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 50px;">* 3 to delete a segment (in this case, variable « tabSeg » is not relevant)</span></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

